<div class="col-xs-12 panel" ng-controller="box3Ctrl" ng-init="init();">
  <h4>Books by author</h4>
  Given an author name the application lists all books written by that author and plots all cities mentioned in any of the books onto a map. Click on a book title to plot the cities mentioned.
  <div class="form-inline">
    <div class="form-group">
      <input type="text" ng-model="author" typeahead-on-select="onAuthorSelected($item, $model, $label, $event)" uib-typeahead="author.name as author.name for author in getAuthors($viewValue)" class="form-control" placeholder="Search author ..." typeahead-loading="loadingAuthors" typeahead-no-results="noResults">
      <i ng-show="loadingAuthors" class="glyphicon glyphicon-refresh"></i>
      <div ng-show="noResults">
        <i class="glyphicon glyphicon-remove"></i> No authors found.
      </div>
    </div>
    <br><br>
  </div>

  <div id="box3_map" class="col-xs-8"></div>
  <div id="occurrences_table" class="col-xs-4">
    <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Title</th>
        </tr>
      <tbody>
        <tr ng-show="!data"><td colspan="100" class="norows">No books to show.</td></tr>
        <tr ng-repeat="(title, cities) in data">
          <td><a ng-click="showOccurrences(cities);">{{title}}</a></td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
      </thead>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>
<%= javascript_include_tag "postgresql/box3_ctrl" %>